  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">In this letter, William Lloyd Garrison and his wife, Helen Eliza Garrison, tell about the death of their dear babe, Elizabeth Pease, who was &quot;ill of a lung fever for a fortnight past.&quot; They would like the presence of the Chapmans and the Westons at the funeral tomorrow.</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">The letter was sent to Mrs. M. W. Chapman, daughter, sisters, and Mary G. Chapman.</subfield>
